    <div class="ym-column linearize-level-1">
        <div class="ym-col1">
            <div class="ym-cbox">
                <section class="box info">
                    
    <h2>Monitor Your Coins</h2>

    <p>We offer a secure payment solution. Unlike other services we don't need access to
        your wallet, and the customers directly pay to your wallet. No need to have bitcoin
        running on your webserver. You only need to provide your Bitcoin addresses and a
        callback url - We will inform you immediately when a payment has been done.</p>
    <p class="box success"><strong>All our services are completely free!</strong></p>
    <p class="box warning">bitcoinmonitor.net is still in (public) betaphase. Please report any bugs, improvement
        suggestions or other feedback <a href="mailto:michael@bitcoinmonitor.net">via mail</a>
        or in the <a target="_blank" href="https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=64195.0">bitcointalk.org</a> forum.</p>
    <a class="ym-button ym-next" href="/services/">Read More</a>

                </section>
                <section class="ym-grid linearize-level-2">
                    <article class="ym-g50 ym-gl">
                        <div class="ym-gbox">
                            
    <h3>Notification Agents</h3>

    <p>You can set up as many notifications agents as you like. Define what actions
        to take at which confirmation level. Available actions right now: Email and url
        callback. Many more actions in the development pipeline!</p>
    <a class="ym-button ym-next" href="/services/#agents">Read More</a>

                        </div>
                    </article>
                    <article class="ym-g50 ym-gr">
                        <div class="ym-gbox">
                            
    <h3>Bitcoin Payment Solution</h3>

    <p>Building up on the notification agents you can easily roll out a flexible
        Bitcoin payment solution. This comes with the benefit of not having to
        expose your bitcoin client to the internet - It can even stay completely
        offline on your home PC!</p>
    <a class="ym-button ym-next" href="/services/#payment">Read More</a>

                        </div>
                    </article>
                </section>
                <section class="ym-grid linearize-level-2">
                    <article class="ym-g50 ym-gl">
                        <div class="ym-gbox">
                            
    <h3>API access</h3>

    <p>Set up and manage your agents both via REST API. This opens up plenty of possibilities to use our service for
        innovative ideas!</p>
    <a class="ym-button ym-next" href="/apidoc/">Read More</a>

                        </div>
                    </article>
                    <article class="ym-g50 ym-gr">
                        <div class="ym-gbox">
                            
    <h3>History</h3>

    <p>We offer a full history of all your notifications, including status, number
        of retries, http result codes from url callback...</p>
    <a class="ym-button ym-next" href="/services/#history">Read More</a>

                        </div>
                    </article>
                </section>
